videos.description: Texas Tech turns the ball over, which leads to Lindy Waters III knocking down a triple plus the foul.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Waters completes 4-point play

videos.description: Justin Gray misses the jumper, but Zhaire Smith follows up with a putback slam.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith flies in for putback jam

videos.description: Zhaire Smith grabs another offensive rebound for the Red Raiders and shows off his bounce with the reverse jam.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith follows miss with reverse dunk

videos.description: Texas Tech turns the ball over, which jumpstarts Oklahoma State's transition leading to Jeffrey Carroll sinking the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Carroll's trey increases Cowboys' run to 14-0

videos.description: Cameron McGriff passes to a cutting Jeffrey Carroll who rocks the rim with two hands for the Cowboys.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Carroll dunks down with authority

videos.description: Oklahoma State guard Tavarius Shine blocks Texas Tech's Zhaire Smith from behind and earns the Cowboys possession of the ball after it goes out of bounds off Smith.
videos.headline: Shine makes pivotal block for Oklahoma State
